data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This tastefully remodeled 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is a haven of modern comfort and style. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this property boasts both a warm, inviting atmosphere and numerous updates that make it move-in ready. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home is conveniently situated near schools, parks, shopping centers, and dining options. With easy access to major thoroughfares, your commute to work or play will be a breeze. Don't miss your chance to make this beautifully remodeled house your forever home
